HolderWeightUpdation_Test
├── when owner deploys the token contract
│   ├── born and holderWeight of owner should be same initially
│   └── born should be equal to the block number of contract deployment
├── when token is transferred
│   ├── it should update the holderWeight of the receiver address equal to source if balance is zero
│   ├── it should update the holderWeight when token is transferred back
│   └── it should update the holderWeight on multiple transfers
└── when returnHolderDelegation is called
    ├── it should return false for unauthorized delegator of caller
    └── it should return true for authorized delegator of caller